org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel

Class HSLFNotes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel.HSLFSheet
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel.HSLFNotes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<HSLFShape>, HSLFShapeContainer, Notes<HSLFShape,HSLFTextParagraph>, ShapeContainer<HSLFShape,HSLFTextParagraph>, Sheet<HSLFShape,HSLFTextParagraph> 

    public final class HSLFNotes
extends HSLFSheet
implements Notes<HSLFShape,HSLFTextParagraph>
    This class represents a slide's notes in a PowerPoint Document. It allows access to the text within, and the layout. For now, it only does the text side of things though(此类代表PowerPoint文档中的幻灯片注释。它允许访问其中的文本和布局。目前，它只处理文本方面的事情)
    Author:
    Nick Burch

      • getPlaceholderDetails

        public HSLFPlaceholderDetails getPlaceholderDetails(Placeholder placeholder)
        Description copied from interface: Sheet
        Get the placeholder details for the given placeholder type. Not all placeholders are also shapes - this is especially true for old HSLF slideshows, which notes have header/footers elements which aren't shapes.(获取给定占位符类型的占位符详细信息。并非所有占位符也是形状-对于旧的HSLF幻灯片显示尤其如此，其中的注释具有不是形状的标题/页脚元素。)
        Specified by:
        getPlaceholderDetails in interface Sheet<HSLFShape,HSLFTextParagraph>(占位符界面工作表中的详细信息)
        Overrides:
        getPlaceholderDetails in class HSLFSheet
        Parameters:
        placeholder - the placeholder type(占位符-占位符类型)
        Returns:
        the placeholder details or null, if the placeholder isn't contained in the sheet(如果占位符不包含在工作表中，则为空)
